PASSED: The House just passed my bill to help expand and improve Small Business Development Centers (SBDCs), which have been crucial to the success of 1000's of Maine small businesses. 375 Democrats and Republicans joined together to push this legislation through. #mepolitics

The 11 SBDC offices across #ME02 offer free business training & advising services to Mainers starting a new small business or trying to grow an existing small biz. SBDCs have helped 1000's of Maine small businesses become successful.
